# AWS Glue Notebook — Per-VIN time-windowed aggregation  (COMPLETE / FINAL)
# Source : Parquet on S3   ->   Output : CSV on S3
# Windows: 15 minutes / 1 hour / 1 day, grouped by metaData_vehicleId + metaData_vin
# Run top to bottom. Edit the two S3 paths in CELL 3. Nothing else to change.
